{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Etymology===
From [[free]] + [[ware]] a contraction of [[software]]; Coined by [[w:Andrew Fluegelman|Andrew Fluegelman]]

===Noun===
'''freeware''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#{{cattag|Computing}}: [[Complete]] and [[functional]] [[software]] that does not require [[payment]] or other [[compensation]] (such as nags or advertising) for its use. Freeware is a proprietary license with no access to the source code.

